This repository is for tools for studying Twitter using probabilistic topic modelling.

## Setup and usage

To do the 'first pass' experiment,

cd first-pass
tar -xzf mallet-2.0.6.tar-gz

then run these scripts in the following order:

getsnowball.py
getLog.py
extract.py
mallet.sh
correlate.py


## Config

To properly configure the scripts in the first-pass/ directory, you need to supply a file, config.cfg, with the following contents:


[OAuth]
accesstoken:realaccesstoken
accesstokenkey:realtokenkey
consumerkey:consumerkey
consumersecret:consumersecret